## Brand Voice & Philosophy

> For Stealth EA's mission, core philosophy, and operating principles, see **CLAUDE.md**. This section focuses on how that philosophy translates into writing and communication style.

### How the Brand Personality Shows Up in Writing

**Seriously Professional, Playfully Irreverent**: Deep expertise delivered with accessibility and wit. Professional credibility that doesn't sacrifice personality. Confidence tempered with humility.

**Stealth by Design**: Let the work speak, not the ego. Comfortable operating behind the scenes. Never loud or self-promoting.

**Anti-Jargon**: Clear communication over buzzword bingo. Explain acronyms, define terms. Accessible language that respects intelligence. Technical precision without unnecessary complexity.

