## Common Mistakes to Avoid

### Content Mistakes

❌ **Over-formatting**:

- Too many bullet points
- Excessive bold text
- Headers every two sentences
- Numbered lists for prose content

✅ **Appropriate formatting**:

- Prose paragraphs for narrative
- Lists only when truly listing items
- Bold for occasional emphasis
- Headers for major section breaks

❌ **Jargon Overload**:

- Undefined acronyms
- Buzzword bingo
- Assuming specialized knowledge
- "Enterprise-grade synergistic leverage"

✅ **Clear Communication**:

- Explain terms in context
- Simple language first
- Technical precision when needed
- Accessible to intelligent non-specialists

❌ **Weak Examples**:

- Abstract theoretical scenarios
- "Imagine a company that..."
- No real-world grounding
- Industry-agnostic generic cases

✅ **Strong Examples**:

- Healthcare or retail specific
- Anonymized client situations
- Real problems and solutions
- Industry patterns and anti-patterns

